## Fearless Concurrency
Rust prevents data races at compile time. 

```rust
use std::thread;
use std::time::Duration;

fn main() {
    let handle = thread::spawn(|| {
        println!("Hello from a thread!");
    });

    handle.join().unwrap(); // Wait for thread to finish
}
```

